document_data.name: Julnar bint Julnar al-Huzuzi
document_data.mainbody: '''Julnar bint Julnar al-Huzuzi''' supervised [[Huzuz]]'s Foreign Bureau in [[1367 DR]].{{AQ-time}}
document_data.Activities: Julnar reported to Ambassador [[Jiraad]], but she directly managed the bureaus of local relations, [[Zakhara]]n relations, and distant relations. She was a competent ambassador and bureaucrat.
